{"tid":1754494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中央批准林鄭月娥辭職","createTime":"2019-11-25T08:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T09:24:42.000Z","uid":230416,"like":6,"dislike":148,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"8b456c74976b08661e7cfb91b129d9640f9d8685","tid":1754494,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:32:57.000Z","msg":"【文匯網訊】據新華社消息，依照香港特別行政區基本法有關規定，根據行政長官梁振英的提名和建議，國務院決定任命張建宗為政務司司長，陳茂波為財政司司長;免去林鄭月娥的政務司司長，曾俊華的財政司司長，張建宗的勞工及福利局局長及陳茂波的發展局局長職務。<br />\n<br />\n預料林鄭月娥在中央公布有關消息後隨即會宣布參選特首。"},{"pid":"eb489c3feaee8c85fe89f11853ed797e7da22347","tid":1754494,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:33:21.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFdd8SA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFdd8SA.png&h=f7682bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fewy8SA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffewy8SA.png&h=4f916815&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZCcnhJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZCcnhJE.jpg&h=155a5ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>投訴 呈請</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n【冇人知】八鄉北點票失誤 鄉事派16票之差勝選 落選人擬提選舉呈請<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754387</a><br />\n[元朗屏山北][搞大佢]區選仲未完仲可以再爭取!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754167</a>"},{"pid":"58b0d664152d9ce536242ae79168c59931192b83","tid":1754494,"uid":186152,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"講漏左,你真係好撚搞笑呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"8a12f9e830152abf19f0ca28ac4bb2cf63f6dee9","tid":1754494,"uid":105201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:33:54.000Z","msg":"pull"},{"pid":"dca5384aa92e0684a2d315